🧮 Step 2: Create Measures (New Measure)
Go to Data pane → Right-click → New measure
Measure 1: Total Sales
Total Sales = SUM(Sales[Sales])
Measure 2: Total Quantity
Total Quantity = SUM(Sales[Quantity])
Measure 3: Average Sales per Order
Avg Sales = AVERAGE(Sales[Sales])
Measure 4: Sales per Quantity
Sales per Qty = DIVIDE([Total Sales], [Total Quantity])
